Package: netra
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, nodejs (>= 16), npm (>= 8)
Description: Modern system architecture visualization tool
 Netra is an interactive system architecture visualization tool
 that displays components and their connections with real-time
 status monitoring and centralized evaluation.
 .
 Features include:
  * Interactive canvas with zoom and pan
  * Real-time status monitoring via HTTP endpoints
  * Centralized evaluation system with shared caching
  * Dynamic connection labels with collision detection
  * Modern glassmorphism UI design
  * System information dialogs with quick links
  * Support for complex component relationships 